<br>
you auto stick saracen<br>
you cast warbellow for 100(-93)<br>
you cast battle howl for 129(-119)<br>
you attack with provoke for 425(-81)<br>
infiltrator dual wields you with garrote for 224 + 73<br>
you mez infiltrator<br>
you attack with provoke for 409(-7<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
infiltrator dual wields you with garrote for 154 + 72<br>
infiltrator dual wields you with no style for 96 + 60<br>
infiltrator dual wields you with 114, second hand no swing<br>
infiltrator dual wields you with garrote for 151, no second hand, + 63 probably proc<br>
<br>
editorial:  that's now 700 damage in 4 swings before my 5.2 hammer recycles<br>
<br>
second infiltrator jumps in, dual wields you with unknown style for 166<br>
you ignore pain for 1159 of your 1432 hits<br>
you attack infl1, he evades<br>
infl1 attacks you for 191 + stun<br>
<br>
at this point i die before stun wears off.  the first infiltrator's final swing was for 299.  my DDs still had 3 seconds to go.  to translate, 1 and a half infiltrators did 2600 damage to me in 17 seconds.  through capped stats on masterpiece armor, against a MELEE class with 6 relics behind him.  infiltrators who were not stealthed when they attacked me.<br>
<br>
i go out and fight friars, reavers, infiltrators, minstrels, paladins, all of which are MUCH better classes than ours.  all of which are auto-lose encounters.  classes i can't beat with 6 relics backing me and perfect spellcrafted armor.  which kill me through IP before my DDs can recycle a single time.<br>
<br>
then i come here and get shouted down that skalds getting shield spec would make us overpowered.  <br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rolleyes --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eyes.gif ALT=":rolleyes"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
where is our 9 second stun on conquer?  and evernight and ragnarok or whatever the sword style is?  where is our 9 second stun on our parry reactionaries?<br>
<br>
why haven't we been given our own skald specific weapon spec which i PERSONALLY took the time to lay out in detail?<br>
<br>
why haven't we been given shield spec and 2.0?<br>
<br>
and most importantly, why do most people here keep saying that evade 2 or a 7% self absorb buff or some such other tiny modification will make the slightest bit of difference when we are facing classes so grossly overpowered compared ours?<br>
<br>
