<br>
#1<br>
<br>
infiltrator attacks 4 times for 700 damage NOT STEALTHED in the time it takes skald to attack once.<br>
<br>
#2<br>
<br>
infiltrator defense works.  skalds have no defense.<br>
<br>
#3<br>
<br>
infiltrators have styles that not only are powerful, they stun.  skalds have none.<br>
<br>
#4<br>
<br>
keep in mind that MIDGARD has all relics on our server.  yet i was outdamaged over time by an UNSTEALTHED stealther.  even if he hadn't evaded a single time (haha chance = 0) i was still being outdamaged over time.<br>
<br>
<br>
SKALDS AND ANY OTHER MELEE SHOULD NOT HAVE TO USE IP TO BEAT AN UNSTEALTHED STEALTHER.  THEY ESPECIALLY SHOULD NOT LOSE TO ONE AFTER USING IP.<br>
<br>
<br>
skalds are underpowered compared to any other melee class in the game on a one on one basis.  the only exceptions are valewalkers due to their craptastic even by our standards styles, and wardens who aren't really a melee.  additionally, skalds bring sub-par support abilities.  skalds have NOTHING.  it is time we got something.<br>
<br>
<br>
